Write a recursive function that returns the sum of the digits of a given integer.
Input format :
Integer N
Output format :
Sum of digits of N
Constraints :
0 <= N <= 10^9




public class solution {

	public static int sumOfDigits(int input){
		// Write your code here
	 if(input<=0){
            return input;
        }
        return input%10+sumOfDigits(input/10);
	

	}
}
